Easily Add Products to Quotes and Orders

Sales reps can directly select products from catalog pages, then create quotes or orders with the selected products. To enable this option, select Product List Page component in Lightning App Builder or Experience Builder, then choose Quote or Order.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.
title: Easily Add Products to Quotes and Orders in Salesforce
